    <Placemark>
      <name>Tempura Yamanoue Roppongi</name>
      <description><![CDATA[<strong>Tempura Yamanoue Roppongi</strong><br/>Tokyo / Akasaka<br/>Cuisine: Tempura<br/>Reservation: Book Instantly<br/>Dinner range: $$$$ JPY 20k-30k<br/>Dinner: JPY 25,000 - 30,000<br/>Lunch range: $$$ JPY 10k-20k<br/>Lunch: JPY 16,000 - 22,000<br/>Summary: Inheriting the spirit and tradition of the legendary Tempura Yamanoue, this Tokyo Midtown restaurant showcases the traditional flavors of tempura to connoisseurs from around the world.<br/><a href="https://pocket-concierge.jp/en/restaurants/244993/?extlink=va-jp-ICS-GMS_LP_en" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Pocket Concierge</a><br/>Approximate location based on public geocoding unless replaced by stronger source matching.]]></description>
